00:34:01,516 --> 00:34:03,636
by linking the MediaPlayer
and iAd frameworks.


769
00:34:03,996 --> 00:34:05,856
Import Media and iAd headers.


770
00:34:05,856 --> 00:34:06,986
You're going to create a player.


771
00:34:07,056 --> 00:34:09,406
You're going to tell it to
