00:34:17,186 --> 00:34:18,536
if you've got your own content.


777
00:34:18,636 --> 00:34:21,016
This is just a few
tiny additional lines.


778
00:34:21,545 --> 00:34:22,846
So what does that look like?


779
00:34:23,065 --> 00:34:25,686
First import MediaPlayer
and import iAd.


780
00:34:26,146 --> 00:34:29,656
You're going to create your
MPMoviePlayerController.


781
00:34:29,846 --> 00:34:30,076
You're going


782
00:34:30,076 --> 00:34:31,985
to initWithContentURL
as you already would.


