00:36:21,136 --> 00:36:23,256
If you're using AVKit
it's almost identical,


831
00:36:23,506 --> 00:36:26,286
AVPlayerController
preparePrerollAds instead.


832
00:36:26,286 --> 00:36:33,346
Going with best practices for
video then: Don't play content


833
00:36:33,656 --> 00:36:34,886
until the ad completes.


